    "These are the Bag of Freebies (BoF) and Bag of Specials (BoS) methods.",
    "Bag of Freebies (BoF) offers different training strategies to the model to increase the detection accuracy of the model or simply increase the training cost and Bag of Specials (BoS) also includes a number of methods that significantly increase object detection accuracy with less computational cost.",
